                            <comment id="62023" author="rstoya05-aop" created="Wed, 5 Jan 2011 10:55:34 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The same request and further suggested approaches in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6437&quot; title=&quot;@MVC should provide an &amp;quot;onBind&amp;quot; hook prior to automatic validation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-6437&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-6437&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="67045" author="rstoya05-aop" created="Fri, 3 Jun 2011 04:48:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Mark, I am resolving this as duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-6437&quot; title=&quot;@MVC should provide an &amp;quot;onBind&amp;quot; hook prior to automatic validation&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SPR-6437&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SPR-6437&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. Please, see &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.springsource.org/browse/SPR-6437?focusedCommentId=48624&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-48624&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;these&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.springsource.org/browse/SPR-6437?focusedCommentId=67042&amp;amp;page=com.atlassian.jira.plugin.system.issuetabpanels:comment-tabpanel#comment-67042&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;two&lt;/a&gt; comments. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Essentially you have two options:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;For controller-specific needs, avoid use of &lt;tt&gt;@Valid&lt;/tt&gt;, inject the validator in the controller, and apply the required logic before validation.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;For needs that apply across controllers, consider configuring a variant of &lt;tt&gt;ServletModelMethodProcessor&lt;/tt&gt;, which provides hooks around data binding and validation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
</comment>
